  <title>How to change the game board size</title>

  <p>You can select a field size at the start of a new game.</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Click <gui style="button">New</gui> or
      <guiseq><gui style="menu">Mines</gui>
      <gui style="menuitem">New Game</gui></guiseq>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>以下からフィールドの大きさを選択します。</p>
      <list>
        <item><p>8 × 8 (地雷10個)</p></item>
        <item><p>16 × 16 (地雷40個)</p></item>
        <item><p>30 × 16 (地雷99個)</p></item>
	<item><p>a custom board, where you chose the size and the number of
	mines</p></item>
      </list>
    </item>
  </steps>

